title: Universal Combat: No CD Key needed, Free Version
description:
This was released in 2005 or 2006 as a free version I believe. Had to seed this FOR GREAT JUSTICE!

Game manuals are included in this. Yes this is a .exe file inside the folder....a GIANT exe file, so no it is not a virus. I d/led this first from some servers the game developers released it on.

Universal Combat allows battle in Land, Air, Sea and Space...lots of variables.
